(13,'HALF-LIFE 2 GOLD','HALF-LIFE 2 GOLD INCLUDES: Half-Life 2 Counter-Strike: Source Half-Life: Source Day of Defeat: Source* Valve''s back catalog available on Steam HALF-LIFE 2 MERCHANDISE: HL2 posters (3 total) HL2 soundtrack HL2 hat HL2 sticker City 17 postcard Prima''s HL2 Strategy Guide Special collector''s box Allow 6-8 weeks for delivery of merchandise included in the Half-Life 2 gold package. * This is an unreleased product and will be made available to purchasers upon its release. The release date for this product is uncertain and purchasers should not rely on any estimated release date. HL2 system requirements','/storefront/images/p50.gif','','$89.95',1,0),
(10,'HALF-LIFE 2 SILVER','HALF-LIFE 2 SILVER INCLUDES: Half-Life 2 Counter-Strike: Source Half-Life: Source Day of Defeat: Source* PLUS: Valve''s back catalog available on Steam * This is an unreleased product and will be made available to purchasers upon its release. The release date for this product is uncertain and purchasers should not rely on any estimated release date. HL2 system requirements','/storefront/images/p51.gif','','$59.95',1,0),
(9,'HALF-LIFE 2 BRONZE','HALF-LIFE 2 BRONZE INCLUDES: Half-Life 2 Counter-Strike: Source HL2 system requirements','/storefront/images/p52.gif','','$49.95',0,0),
(7,'CONDITION ZERO','CONDITION ZERO INCLUDES: Counter-Strike: Condition Zero Condition Zero Deleted Scenes Counter-Strike Multiplayer Counter-Strike&trade;: Condition Zero&trade; features all of the award winning-games in the Counter-Strike franchise. Log onto the world''s number 1 online action game. Play online or offline with the official CS Bot. Or enjoy the single player Deleted Scenes.','/storefront/images/p43.gif','','$29.95',0,0),
(8,'VALVE PREMIER PACK','VALVE PREMIER PACK INCLUDES: Half-Life Half-Life: Opposing Force Day of Defeat Team Fortress Classic Deathmatch Classic Ricochet With six incredible games from Valve, including Half-Life and Day of Defeat, the Valve Premier Pack is an incredible value at just $19.95. Included products are a mix of single player and multiplayer games. Order your copy now.&nbsp;','/storefront/images/p44.gif','/storefront/images/screen_premier.gif','$34.95',0,0);
